data.description: Discover Your Dream Home in Idaho Falls, Idaho! This remarkable 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom residence is a testament to elegance and modernity. Set on an expansive lot just under 0.5 acres, this property showcases an array of impressive features. Inside, you'll find a harmonious blend of old-world charm and contemporary updates. Newer wiring and partially updated plumbing ensure peace of mind, while fresh carpet, refinished floors, and all-new paint create a bright, welcoming atmosphere. The bathrooms have been artfully renovated, with the master bath boasting a stunning tiled shower with gold accents and a double sink vanity. Two living rooms, two family rooms, and a gas fireplace with brick accents provide plenty of space for relaxation and entertainment. Outdoors, a lush, established lawn complements a 2-car garage and a 25 x 20 detached shop with 220 power and a wood-burning stove – a dream workspace for hobbyists. This Idaho Falls gem offers a rare blend of modern comfort and timeless appeal. Make it yours today!
